casebody.data:
No. 646. Elizabeth J. Ward, Petitioner, v. Dampskibsselskabet Kjoebenhavn. April 8, 1907. Mr. Frank R. Savidge for petitioner. Mr. J. Parker Kirlin and Mr. C. R. Hickox for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
